FACILITY WORDS
==============


MS                ( milliseconds# -- )
                  Wait at least the specified milliseconds
                  (suspend the forth tasklet)

RANDOM            ( -- x )
                  Generate a random number.
             See: SEED.

SEED              ( x -- )
                  Initialize the random number generator.
             See: RANDOM.

NOW               ( -- sec# min# hrs# day# month# year# )
                  Return the broken down current time.
             See: .NOW.

.NOW              ( sec# min# hrs# day# month# year# -- )
                  Display date and time in ISO 8601 format without the time zone.
             See: NOW.

